{"about_the_game":"<strong>Plates of Peril</strong> is a dark <strong>dungeon-cooking</strong> game where you gather ingredients, prepare dishes, and serve them to demanding customers. <u><i>Play solo or team up with up to 3 friends</i></u> as you survive the chaos to <strong>become the ultimate chef in a dungeon full of danger.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3451820/extras/pop_explore_store.png?t=1737298406\" /><br><strong>Explore the procedurally generated dungeons to gather ingredients for your dishes.<br>But watch out for traps, and be careful, you'll never know who or what is hiding.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3451820/extras/pop_cook_store.png?t=1737298406\" /><br><strong>Combine your ingredients to make unique dishes and boost your reputation as a chef of the dungeon!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3451820/extras/pop_boss_store.png?t=1737298406\" /><br><strong>Occasionally, your boss will drop by for a taste test.<br>Serve perfection, or suffer the consequences.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3451820/extras/pop_friends_store.png?t=1737298406\" /><br><strong>Team up with up to 3 friends in chaotic co-op gameplay!<br>Work together to gather ingredients, cook dishes, and survive the dungeon\u2019s peril.<br>Who is the best chef?</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3451820/extras/pop_buffs_store.png?t=1737298406\" /><br><strong>Instead of serving food to customers, eat your favorite foods for strategic stat boosts.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3451820/extras/pop_replayability_store.png?t=1737